# Payment Service

Microservice for processing payments in UshaSree Industries.

## Endpoints

- **POST /payment** — Make payment for order
- **GET /payment/:userId** — Get all payments by user

## Environment Variables

See `.env.example` for required values.

## Docker

```sh
docker build -t <your-dockerhub>/ushasree-payment:latest .
docker run -p 3005:3005 --env-file .env <your-dockerhub>/ushasree-payment:latest
